11.name: S.S. 'Coptic'
11.description: "Continuation of the above picture [S.S. COPTIC LYING TO]. Sun bursts forth, silver tipping the foam on the wave crests. The billows surge grandly."

18.name: Masked Procession
18.description: "Masqueraders dressed in most grotesque costumes are passing one side of the grandstand, while a procession of bicyclists wheel by on the other side."
